@startuml seq_02_google_sign_in
title Sequence Diagram: UC-02.2 Sign In (Google OAuth)

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Auth Controller" as Controller
participant "Auth Service" as Service
participant "Google OAuth" as Google
participant "User Repository" as Repo
participant "Redis Cache" as Redis

User -> Frontend: Click "Login with Google"
Frontend -> Controller: GET /api/auth/google/login
Controller --> Frontend: Redirect to Google Consent Screen
Frontend -> Google: Redirect User
User -> Google: Authorize application
Google --> Frontend: Redirect to callback URL with Auth Code
Frontend -> Controller: GET /api/auth/google/callback?code=...
Controller -> Service: Process Google Callback
Service -> Google: Exchange Auth Code for Tokens
Google --> Service: Google Access Token
Service -> Google: Fetch User Profile
Google --> Service: Profile Data (Email, Name, Avatar)
Service -> Repo: Find User by Google ID or Email
alt User exists
    Repo --> Service: Existing User
else User not found
    Service -> Repo: Create new User
    Repo --> Service: New User created
end
Service -> Service: Generate Access & Refresh Tokens
Service -> Redis: Store Auth State (Refresh Token)
Service --> Controller: Tokens & User Info
Controller --> Frontend: Redirect to Home with Tokens
Frontend --> User: Display Home Page
@enduml